{"tid":788484,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"醜小鴨變天鵝！「韓國第一美女」金喜善9歲女近照瘋傳","createTime":"2018-08-21T13:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T05:24:22.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"52b3fcfb6f1427b8599328a8b7a5f91fa5da0718","tid":788484,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-08-21/656/20180821003895.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-08-21%2F656%2F20180821003895.jpg&h=eb1bb24b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金喜善曾因女兒長相被批評醜，一度萌生移民念頭。<br />\n<br />\n被譽為韓國第一美女的金喜善，當年在事業最高峰的時候嫁給了長相帥氣的富二代朴周永，婚後生下寶貝女兒朴妍雅，後來卻因為女兒顏值與她差很大，讓她被網友質疑整形，讓金喜善坦言後悔公開女兒照片，甚至有了移民念頭，「我是藝人，我的女兒就得挨駡嗎？第一次後悔當藝人，甚至都不想生活在這個國家！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-08-21/450/20180821003903.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-08-21%2F450%2F20180821003903.jpg&h=13b9328e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-08-21/450/20180821003905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-08-21%2F450%2F20180821003905.jpg&h=d5d63b09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金喜善女兒照片突然在網路瘋傳，甚有媽媽的影子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBM9rkZ.img?h=416&amp;w=799&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;u=t&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=493&amp;y=196\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBM9rkZ.img%3Fh%3D416%26w%3D799%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26u%3Dt%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D493%26y%3D196&h=6e601f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開季兩連勝的曼城，以得失球優勢，位居榜首。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-08-21/450/20180821003921.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-08-21%2F450%2F20180821003921.jpg&h=7f6a1d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金喜善全家福。<br />\n<br />\n然而今日陸網突然瘋傳一張號稱是金喜善9歲女兒的近照，一雙靈活大眼睛加肉嘟嘟的臉蛋看起來十分可愛，像極了金喜善小時候的模樣，完全印證了女大18變這句話，網友們也驚艷大讚「小時候只是五官還沒長開」、「張開了還是漂亮的啊，為啥之前噴的人那麼多」、「這真的是同一個小孩嗎」、「女大十八變，越變越好看」。"},{"pid":"437b2869b1278f21f2356df6d4869374c2537671","tid":788484,"uid":116547,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"幾似哥迪奧拿"},{"pid":"2ec2b76b16aeab0ec95c2b1fa6f8491c0cbf27e9","tid":788484,"uid":100136,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"Genes don&rsquo;t lie"},{"pid":"47f4181a2a1633fb99f2e236eb44c7020828bf7e","tid":788484,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:51:04.000Z","msg":"有乜所謂<br />\n<br />\n個老豆老母都整㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442ac53a2c8214f24d89b8fafea55d0c8169e29d","tid":788484,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:51:08.000Z","msg":"對眼似老豆"},{"pid":"3bb2fac8e9ebddfc4a5767d2cb83c4ae85e501ee","tid":788484,"uid":141656,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:52:33.000Z","msg":"成年後一定靚<br />\n因為佢阿媽阿爸一定比錢佢大整"},{"pid":"22140408a5b3d107d945ee11674e64f0b521e5d8","tid":788484,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:55:25.000Z","msg":"咪一樣唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1eba36dbe529e179b0904adfb28bdd71866d70","tid":788484,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:42:01.000Z","msg":"整既咋嘛 屌你老母"},{"pid":"2c6e142c8ca7c99d8f465eb18f9bf12f4fe2b4c2","tid":788484,"uid":130897,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:43:29.000Z","msg":"關曼城咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ba007a6266af502939b4ed8c35aaae372a2592","tid":788484,"uid":84619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:43: